.online/publication/lessons-for-europe-from-the-2008-icelandic-bank-collapse1 ''Lessons for Europe from the 2008 Icelandic Bank Collapse.''] New Direction, Brussels 2017. * [http://newdirection.online/publication/green-capitalism-how-to-protect-the-environment-by-defining-private-propert ''Green Capitalism: How to Protect the Environment by Defining Private Property Rights.''] New Direction, Brussels 2017. * ''Totalitarianism in Europe: Three Case Studies.'' ACRE, Brussels 2018.
